"Template" orange texture pack is for prototyping map layout design 
without worrying about the textures. The files can be used in level editors 
like GTK Radiant (or NetRadiant or DarkRadiant) or Blender.
Special thanks to evillair for his 'Template' textures, which inspired this.
http://evillair.net/v3/pages/downloads.php

"Template" orange texture pack by cron is released as CC0 1.0 Universal (CC0 1.0)
